做，中午要送出街，我同TB打仗咁，9點正垃圾女上司叫我地入房，放低自己野幫佢手，得我開聲撐話要做左deadline 野先，廢物TB！<br />\n<br />\n安排工作又係九流，之後又上左幾日大陸做樣本展示又要乜，我第一次見跟單要做咁L多嘢，個倉又亂到乜，想拎樣本都搵唔到！我又要執返好，不過我主動，冇所謂。<br />\n<br />\n大陸廠寄樣本又全部寫我名收，其他team屌鬼咁，關我q事咩，晩晚收9點，之後即resign!<br />\n<br />\n2個月之後公司忽然摺左，好彩走得快<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76201a44a52a8148279e42486136bbe474faa61d","tid":1173633,"uid":173264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T15:52:14.000Z","msg":"試過有份工 病咗講病假 聲都沙哂<br />\n老細打嚟係咁單打 話如果見工就直接講<br />\n唔好浪費大家時間 唔洗扮病咁慘喎<br />\n<br />\n老女人特別多疑 cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df11a2d6b42de817083cf1441bb48eecd191739","tid":1173633,"uid":229095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"199497a175fccf09fe0e40a1d6027e31875aa441","tid":1173633,"uid":62289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7c88d4daf8ad00c2ff1ce462dd48fbca6c42580","tid":1173633,"uid":229095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T09:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T12:09:54.000Z","msg":"人工幾多先？ 同事閪真係好難頂 <br />\n我而家個份 同事唔會放暗箭 <br />\n但教野又講勁快 筆記都記唔切<br />\n人工又得13k"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T16:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}